---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Blog
description: Shorter cadence — notes, updates, and things we built recently for service businesses.
permalink: /blog/
---

<section class="hero-lite"><div class="wrap">
  <div class="ey">The firm</div>
  <h1 class="h1">Blog</h1>
  <p class="lead">Shorter posts. Things we built, what we're thinking about, and updates from the firm.</p>
</div></section>

<section class="section post-rows"><div class="wrap">

  {% if collections.blog.length > 0 %}
    {% for post in collections.blog | reverse %}
      <a class="post-row" href="{{ post.url }}">
        <div class="post-row-meta">
          <span class="post-row-date">{{ post.date | date }}</span>
          <span class="post-row-tag">Post</span>
        </div>
        <div class="post-row-body">
          <h2 class="post-row-h">{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
          {% if post.data.summary %}<p>{{ post.data.summary }}</p>{% endif %}
          <span class="post-row-more">Read &#8594;</span>
        </div>
      </a>
    {% endfor %}
  {% else %}
    <p class="muted">No posts published yet.</p>
  {% endif %}

</div></section>
